com.fluidops.fedx.structures

Interface EndpointConfiguration

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    SparqlEndpointConfiguration

    public interface EndpointConfiguration
    Additional marker interface for Endpoint Configurations. An EndpointConfiguration may bring additional configuration settings for an Endpoint, e.g. in the case of a SparqlTripleSource it may decide whether ASK or SELECT queries shall be used for source selection.
    Author:
    Andreas Schwarte
